News.Title: DBCE ACM Chapter Tour to Jaipur
News.Description: The DBCE ACM Chapter of Don Bosco College of Engineering took a tour to Jaipur to learn about various industries, explore the city's cultural heritage, and visit famous forts and tourist attractions.

News.Title: DBCE ACM Organises A Poster Competition....
News.Description: Don Bosco College of Engineering under DBCE ACM student chapter organized Poster Making Competition for students of Government High School, Balli Goa under senior(Standard VIII-X) and junior category (Standard V-VII) on 24th September 2022.
